<paragraph blockId="73.[151,1436,1372,1592]" pageId="73" pageNumber="74">
Several specimens have unusually high numbers of pinnae, 9–15 versus the more usual 3–5. Specimens from Volcan Arenal (
<emphasis box="[400,727,1566,1592]" italics="true" pageId="73" pageNumber="74">Russell 683, 893, Lent 3335</emphasis>
) have larger leaves and inflorescences than the others.
</paragraph>
